novamin board to recommend breakwater <bwrlf> bid
    vancouver, british columbia, april 1 - 
<novamin inc> said its board will recommend to shareholders the
takeover offer made by breakwater resources ltd. breakwater is
offering to exchange one breakwater share for each two shares of
novamin, the company said. breakwater will issue about 3.7 mln shares
for all novamin shares presently issued and outstanding. additional
shraes of breakwater will be issued if warrants and options of novamin
are exercised. reuter 
